96
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,000
Caixi.

97
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,070
Tell me about him.

98
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:37,870
Come with me.

99
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:51,070
