130
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:36,550
All right.

131
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,000
Stop reading it.

132
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,200
Caixi.

133
00:10:39,870 --> 00:10:40,630
It’s enough.

134
00:10:40,790 --> 00:10:41,630
All right.

135
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:44,840
It’s okay.

136
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,790
Let him read it.

137
