and my mom by my side.

165
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:50,550
Are you going crazy again?

166
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,080
Go away!

167
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:56,030
It’s too gross!

168
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,120
Go away!

169
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:05,720
