170
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,200
Let me give you a hug. Come on.

171
00:13:07,510 --> 00:13:08,750
Come on.

172
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:13,080
Tell me what happened today.

173
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,910
-Mom.
-Well?

174
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,470
When Grandpa died,

175
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:21,510
