176
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:22,600
What?

177
00:13:25,870 --> 00:13:28,080
Why do you ask this suddenly?

178
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:30,080
My good friend’s father passed away.

179
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,440
I don’t know how to comfort her.

180
00:13:35,270 --> 00:13:37,270
Her family passed away,

181
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,550
