182
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:43,270
Actually, it’s no use
no matter how you comfort her.

183
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:45,810
You’d better

184
00:13:45,810 --> 00:13:48,030
just stay by her side.

185
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,720
Don’t ask too many questions.

186
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:52,550
It would be the best

187
00:13:52,550 --> 00:13:54,320
