188
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,550
that can distract her.

189
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:59,360
Or you can cook something she likes.

190
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:04,030
That’s how your dad
comforted me at that time.

191
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,840
Yeah.

192
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:09,030
Tell me what your monitor likes to eat.

193
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,150
She loves chicken wings.

194
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,390
Scrambled eggs with tomatoes.

195
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:14,910
-Cabbage.
-Yeah.

196
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,750
Anything else?

197
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,910
