when you raise your butt.

200
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:26,910
Mom, you are impressive.

201
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:36,840
It’s getting late.
You two go to bed earlier.

202
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,550
-Okay.
-Okay.

203
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,960
Good night.

204
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,630
I wish there is a time machine

205
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,480
that can let me see Dad again.

206
00:14:52,030 --> 00:14:53,870
Dad will be pissed off

207
00:14:54,080 --> 00:14:55,390
to see you like this.

208
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,030
Well?

209
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:09,240
Caixi, what’s this?

210
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:12,550
Nothing. I hit the desk today.

211
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:14,000
Don’t scare me.

212
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,790
