when he was sick.

213
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,120
The bruises...

214
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:20,840
Caixi.

215
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:22,550
Won’t you have leukemia?

216
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:24,510
