218
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:27,550
Go back to sleep.

219
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,790
Then I can rest assured.

220
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,960
Remember what you said.
You must stay alive to that time.

221
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:34,480
Okay.

222
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,630
-Not a minute less.
-I got it.

223
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:36,720
I will outlive you.

224
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,670
-Okay, good night.
-Good night.

225
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:27,960
-Yuan Caixi!
-Ugh...

226
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:39,600
Let’s go.

227
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,870
Wait, Yuan.

228
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:42,080
Are you okay?

229
00:16:43,550 --> 00:16:44,960
-Yuan!
-Yuan Caixi!

230
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:49,480
