too tired and undernourished recently.

233
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:58,850
Yuan Caixi, are you okay?

234
00:16:58,930 --> 00:17:00,150
Do you feel dizzy again?

235
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:06,070
I have a poor appetite recently
and feel dizzy and tired.

236
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:09,720
And the bruises won’t heal
for a long time.

237
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:11,880
I guess it’s leukemia.

238
00:17:12,590 --> 00:17:14,790
Leukemia is too scary.

239
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:44,720
(Yuan Caixi)

240
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:46,300
Tell me, is the traitor Ning Zeyu

241
00:17:46,300 --> 00:17:48,070
or Han Yayi?

242
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:53,590
(Li He)

243
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:56,310
Well, why can’t I be telepathic?

244
00:18:03,070 --> 00:18:04,630
Can you use your telepathy

245
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:06,240
to know today is my dad’s birthday

246
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:08,920
and come to comfort me
because you don’t want me to feel sad?

247
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,790
Don’t underestimate the IQ
of the world champion.

248
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:32,440
World champion, you should go to sleep.
Good night.

249
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:40,720
Monitor, I’ve always been there.

250
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:58,440
Okay, I know.

251
00:20:23,510 --> 00:20:24,960
Well, monitor.

252
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,350
Are you also going to the clinic?

253
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,790
No, I’m going to the toilet.

254
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:28,880
Oh, I’m gonna go.

255
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:29,960
-Okay.
-Bye.

256
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:45,920
Come in.

257
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:53,000
Hello, what can I help you?

258
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,110
I have something to ask you.

259
00:20:57,110 --> 00:20:57,830
Okay.

260
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,960
-I have a friend...
-Oh.

261
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,750
You have a friend.

262
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:08,110
I have a friend

263
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:10,030
who has a poor appetite.

264
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:12,590
She always feels dizzy and falls easily.

265
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:15,110
The most important thing is
that she got a lot of bruises on her.

266
00:21:16,030 --> 00:21:16,960
Where? Let me see.

267
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,200
It’s not me.

268
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:19,480
It’s a friend of mine.

269
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:22,200
Okay, then tell me about

270
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:24,590
the bruises on your friend.

271
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:28,030
